{"tid":657484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門觀塘巴打小心家中老友記","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T10:00:36.000Z","uid":152315,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d1e82ba363adefa9af19d7559f1ae5b590cac8","tid":657484,"uid":152315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"屯門開左間田園,專棍老人家買孝素<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/145117_74e778db3ebccc6b9e574accecf62bd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F145117_74e778db3ebccc6b9e574accecf62bd4.png&h=8fe984e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/145121_d2ea404fe83b6a4e72f5c2212a26d707.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F145121_d2ea404fe83b6a4e72f5c2212a26d707.png&h=d8b597f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/145122_763dc286ee731267897473dec0e3f1be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F145122_763dc286ee731267897473dec0e3f1be.png&h=de2bda83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/145123_c80e37464ebc9481e5d3c4d2318f3113.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F145123_c80e37464ebc9481e5d3c4d2318f3113.png&h=20cbb131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全部人都好似洗左腦咁,就因我老母買左好多,今日就去睇下,個啊婆同我講,你好孝順,買孝素比老母,心諗唔能係呀麻,我想黎係踼爆...點知..排隊入場,個濕九職員話我無卡,唔比入,我唯有企門口,,聽能到班友係咁sell腦孝素..又話觀塘開新鋪..所以觀塘巴打睇實老人家,我老母已比洗腦,求巴打教路"},{"pid":"9c62c2fc8ae8d1e32c9ccb071c1707db1e6735dd","tid":657484,"uid":42182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"新墟"},{"pid":"f0bb763dbf2b09e1fc2ae656c57aa3e9d4672cd7","tid":657484,"uid":152315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c62c2fc8ae8d1e32c9ccb071c1707db1e6735